    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable dents, and areas of fading paint. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and several interior components show signs of damage or are non-functional. Mechanically, the car runs but needs immediate repairs to be considered reliable for daily use. This is an ideal project car for someone looking to put in the work or a budget-friendly option for those with the tools to restore it.",
