    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. Meticulously cared for and flawless inside and out, it offers a truly premium driving experience for someone who settles for nothing but the best. Don't miss out on this rare find!",
      "price": 48500.0,
